name: We Thr33 Queens
description:
There were no numbers.
Their Divinity was pure and sacred geometry.

The wholesome light that shone from their cheeks was admired by friend and foe alike.

"We are Oneness"
"We are Love"
"Commune and endure no pain or fear."

Upon the firmness of trust in our heart, may you lay your head and rest forever.

We three Queens are complete blessings unto you.
